org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.publication.services

Class RecipientProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.publication.services.RecipientProcessor

  • @Component
public class RecipientProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows computation of the three following things for an input Recipient :
    • The list of concerned groups
    • The list of concerned orphan users (concerned users not belonging to any concerned group)
    • The main recipient if any. The main recipient is the responsible user for the associated card
